{"tid":1243923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個特首既面子重要啲定香港人既面子重要啲？","createTime":"2019-06-19T16:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T16:51:24.000Z","uid":103672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"70548c33c4406312ad6fc7a2d124994860b65a81","tid":1243923,"uid":103672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"屌身邊好多朋友都好似開始唔再關心呢件事，覺得佢道咗歉同話今個立法年度唔再推就算。屌佢為咗個面子就死都唔係講撤回兩個字，為咗面子着返之前贏選舉既衫出黎黑面同香港人道歉。有啲人話：算啦佢都係要個下台階要面子啫。算？我算你老母呀！而家二百萬人上街，果五個訴求一個都達唔到呀。講冇面係佢冇面定香港人冇面呀？外國既話一個二百萬人示威真係可以搞到個政府倒台。而喺香港呢？好！行完散水！你話好唔好笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今舖真係做國際笑話。仲想為香港人挽回面子既話星期五知點做啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb4d997bf97d74ee2a942826c3f916471365378","tid":1243923,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c9039b9d2227c341d4d9041f16fb5831f2232f0","tid":1243923,"uid":103672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0f5178e4e78890e5544311c9b5084c5625d194","tid":1243923,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"都不重要"},{"pid":"44030a0ebaed7d19d167bba416f4962ab1ddc18a","tid":1243923,"uid":222712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7tnCE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7tnCE1.png&h=81c2acbe&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}